node.text: We took Grammy nominated Steinway artist Vincent Corver and asked him to play for us on this $1million piano painted by @alecmonopoly We placed it inside the stunning @ultimacollection Grand Villa Geneva, surrounded by some of the finest vintage and modern cars from the collection of @rebelliontimepieces.
Two spectacular Eastern Arabic Day Dates sandwiching a NOS Serpico y Laino Datejust 🥪 and that’s before we get to the insane bracelets..! Thanks @momentumdubai
